attribute.value: The Bambara tee is made with a light weave of pure cotton. Just throw it on an go. Available in a variety of sizes and colors, this is the ideal utility tee. Everyone should have half a dozen of these!

• Light weight 100% cotton
  • Odor-resistent
  • Available in five colors: sandstorm brown, fire engine red, sky blue, ice white and obsidian black
  • Easy-wash: Guaranteed not to shrink in the dryer
  • Double stitched for durability
  • Available in sizes XS to XXL

Specially engineered for a woman's foot. These cross-trainers provide impact resistance with lateral support. Suitable for both track and court.

• Extra lateral support
  • Quick fasten velcro
  • Elasticized upper for maximum comfort
An everyday runner that provides excellent support and comfort. Features the Geometrixx Impacto cushioning system.

• Lightweight upper with mesh windows for ventilation
  • Impacto cusioning system delivers 30% more protection when running on hard surfaces
  • Excellent ankle support
  • Available in a variety of colors

The Saskatoon parka provides maximum protection in the coldest of weather. A storm shell combined with high-loft goose down ensures excellent protection from the elements, with the fur-lined hood keeping the wind and snow from your face.

• Storm shell provides wind and rain protection while allowing moisture to escape, keeping you warm and dry
  • High loft goose down provides the best lightweight insulation.
  • Fur-lined hood for great protection in high wind conditions
  • Two high hand warmer pockets with fleece lining and two lower fleece lined pockets to keep your hands warm
  • Heavy duty rib knit cuffs and waistband to keep out cold winds and drafts
  • Inset sleeve design for comfort and improved fit

The Ashanti is a great looking tee made from high-quality, durable material. We have put this shirt through a battery of tests and it has stood up well: no shrinking, staining or fading. The medium-weight fabric keeps its shape well and retains a soft comfortable feel even after many washings. The fit is relaxed for all-day wear. Soft jersey-knit taping on the neck seam. Straight hem. Durable double-needle stitching. Tagless printed label for added comfort. 6 oz. jersey-knit fabric. Imported. Machine wash and dry.

• Medium weight 99-to-1 cotton/lycra blend
  • Uses our patented "wick-weave" design
  • Odor-resistant
  • Available in five colors: sandstorm brown, fire engine red, sky blue, ice white and obsidian black
  • "No-tags". No annoying tags to scratch or catch
  • Easy-wash- Guaranteed not to shrink in the dryer
  • Double stitched for durability
  • Available in sizes XS to XXL
100% New Zealand wool poncho with shoulder clasp. Soft and non-scratchy. Perfect for cool autumn days.

• 100% wool
  • Made in New Zealand
  • Double shoulder clasp

The Calgary wommen's winter coat is insulated with goose down to keep you warm even on the coldest days. A breatable water-resistant outer shell keeps you dry and keeps the wind out.

• Nylon outer shell provides wind and rain protection while allowing moisture to escape, keeping you warm and dry
  • High loft goose down provides the best lightweight insulation.
  • High collar for warmth and protection
  • Available in avariety of bright colors
The most technical gloves we offer. With Nortex protection on the outside and Superfleece warmth on the inside.

• Nortex outer shell provides wind and rain protection while allowing moisture to escape, keeping your hands warm and dry
  • Superfleece lining provide 50% better insulation that standard fleece
  • Long uppers to cover wrist and ensure that no snow gets in
